{"id": "art-97", "label": "Art. 97", "title": "Art. 97: Proba şi mijloacele de probă", "slug": "art-97", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 97: Proba &#351;i mijloacele de prob&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Constituie prob&#259; orice\nelement de fapt care serve&#351;te la constatarea existen&#355;ei sau\ninexisten&#355;ei unei infrac&#355;iuni, la identificarea persoanei care a\ns&#259;vâr&#351;it-o &#351;i la cunoa&#351;terea împrejur&#259;rilor necesare pentru\njusta solu&#355;ionare a cauzei &#351;i care contribuie la aflarea\nadev&#259;rului în procesul penal.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Proba se ob&#355;ine în procesul penal prin urm&#259;toarele mijloace:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>a)declara&#355;iile\nsuspectului sau ale inculpatului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)declara&#355;iile\npersoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)declara&#355;iile\np&#259;r&#355;ii civile sau ale p&#259;r&#355;ii responsabile civilmente;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)declara&#355;iile\nmartorilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_535492025\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2598\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_535492025\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)înscrisuri, rapoarte de expertiz&#259; sau constatare,\nprocese-verbale, fotografii, mijloace materiale de prob&#259;;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>f)orice\nalt mijloc de prob&#259; care nu este interzis prin lege.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1448325648\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2597\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1448325648\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Procedeul probatoriu este modalitatea legal&#259; de\nob&#355;inere a mijlocului de prob&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}